name: Leonardo Da Vinci (Psychic Portraits)
description:
This artwork was entirely created by using Da Vinci’s self portrait like it was paint & brush at the same time, multiplied thousands of times. Nothing else was added. I call my technique "transfiguration".

As most of my art, it’s about summoning spirits from images and me acting as a medium for them to emerge, guided by my own intuition and aesthetic sense.

This short video will take you inside this artwork (original in 4K), to explore its details: https://youtu.be/0cqcz6qEMSU
